Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1050)\fad(800,800)}真的很抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约定好的吗 只要是我能做到的都能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:24:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是梦呢 快点起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.14,0:24:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我们是一家人呢
